<前言><![CDATA[]]></前言>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This set of criteria is formulated in accordance with regulations of Paragraph 4, Article 21 of the HIV Infection Control and Patient Rights Protection Act.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The scope of unsafe sexual behavior refers to sexual behavior that involves direct contact with the mucous membranes of organs or body fluids without isolation and has been medically assessed as having a significant risk of infection and causing HIV infection.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This set of criteria shall be implemented on the day of announcement.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
